in the dialysis clinic.

1561
01:30:19,747 --> 01:30:21,833
You know, I have to say that
over the last few months,

1562
01:30:22,333 --> 01:30:24,786
he's been doing very well.

1563
01:30:24,786 --> 01:30:26,287
His blood pressure's
under control,

1564
01:30:26,287 --> 01:30:28,589
he's taking better
care of himself,

1565
01:30:28,589 --> 01:30:29,874
and one of my cardiology
colleagues recently informed me

1566
01:30:29,874 --> 01:30:33,761
