1567
01:30:33,761 --> 01:30:36,214
The good news is a donor
match has been confirmed

1568
01:30:36,214 --> 01:30:37,548
for Christopher.

1569
01:30:37,548 --> 01:30:39,016
Oh, thank the Lord.

1570
01:30:39,016 --> 01:30:41,853
What's required now, doctor?

1571
01:30:41,853 --> 01:30:43,771
Only that he receive it.

1572
01:30:43,771 --> 01:30:44,772
We want to begin surgery
