1592
01:31:40,328 --> 01:31:43,331
Christopher Bauman.

1593
01:31:43,831 --> 01:31:47,201
We will definitely keep him
in prayer for a speedy recovery.

1594
01:31:47,201 --> 01:31:48,586
You have a very
