1652
01:35:15,493 --> 01:35:17,995
(Sarah)
Dear Christopher,
Merry Christmas.

1653
01:35:17,995 --> 01:35:20,998
I'm glad to know
you're recovering well.

1654
01:35:21,499 --> 01:35:23,000
Your mother showed me
a Scripture that read,

1655
01:35:23,000 --> 01:35:27,004
"With God, all things
are possible."

1656
01:35:27,004 --> 01:35:30,508
Christopher, I do believe all
things are possible with God,

1657
01:35:31,008 --> 01:35:32,510
including our marriage.

1658
01:35:32,510 --> 01:35:34,512
Can we talk?

1659
01:35:34,512 --> 01:35:36,981
Please get well soon.

1660
01:35:36,981 --> 01:35:40,818
Willing to forgive, Sarah.

1661
01:35:43,654 --> 01:35:46,607
[knocking on door]

1662
01:35:48,609 --> 01:35:49,110
Knock, knock.

1663
01:35:49,610 --> 01:35:51,612
Merry Christmas, son.

1664
01:35:52,113 --> 01:35:52,613
Hi, Mom.

1665
01:35:52,613 --> 01:35:53,614
Merry Christmas to you too.

1666
01:35:53,614 --> 01:35:55,533
How do you feel?

1667
01:35:55,533 --> 01:35:57,451
Just tired.

1668
01:35:57,451 --> 01:35:58,869
But I don't remember anything.

1669
01:35:58,869 --> 01:36:02,456
Well, you just remember
this, God has blessed you

1670
01:36:02,456 --> 01:36:03,457
with a donated kidney.

1671
01:36:03,457 --> 01:36:05,926
That is a great
Christmas present.

1672
01:36:06,427 --> 01:36:09,346
I'd say it makes for
an amazing Christmas gift,

1673
01:36:09,346 --> 01:36:10,264
Christopher.

1674
01:36:10,264 --> 01:36:11,766
Thanks, doc.

1675
01:36:11,766 --> 01:36:13,384
Don't thank me,
thank your mom.

1676
01:36:13,384 --> 01:36:15,219
I truly believe that if it had
not been for her strong faith

1677
01:36:15,219 --> 01:36:18,222
and prayers, your situation
would have turned out

1678
01:36:18,222 --> 01:36:19,356
for the worse.

1679
01:36:25,062 --> 01:36:27,064
(male #11)
All rise for
the Honorable Judge King.

1680
01:36:27,565 --> 01:36:31,068
Thank you.
You may be seated.

1681
01:36:34,071 --> 01:36:36,323
Thank you.

1682
01:36:40,127 --> 01:36:44,965
Divorce court 1023,
case number 1001,

1683
01:36:44,965 --> 01:36:48,886
Sarah Bauman versus
Christopher Bauman.

1684
01:36:48,886 --> 01:36:51,806
Are you the attorney
representing Sarah Bauman?

1685
01:36:52,306 --> 01:36:53,808
Yes, Your Honor.

1686
01:36:53,808 --> 01:36:55,726
Where's your client?

1687
01:36:55,726 --> 01:36:59,396
Well, Your Honor,
I'm not certain.

1688
01:36:59,396 --> 01:37:02,399
I've represented many families
going through what I now realize

1689
01:37:02,399 --> 01:37:06,821
to be a tragedy and never
thought for more than a moment

1690
01:37:06,821 --> 01:37:10,691
the harm that
perhaps I've caused.

1691
01:37:10,691 --> 01:37:12,776
So yesterday, as I sat
down with my client,

1692
01:37:12,776 --> 01:37:15,279
I gave her different
words, living Words.

1693
01:37:15,279 --> 01:37:18,616
I shared with her
this Scripture.

1694
01:37:19,116 --> 01:37:22,169
It says that tribulation
produces perseverance,

1695
01:37:22,670 --> 01:37:25,923
and perseverance character,
and character hope,

1696
01:37:26,257 --> 01:37:29,093
and now hope does
not disappoint.

1697
01:37:29,093 --> 01:37:30,961
Okay, one moment.

1698
01:37:30,961 --> 01:37:31,846
This is not church.

1699
01:37:31,846 --> 01:37:34,215
This is a court of law.

1700
01:37:34,215 --> 01:37:37,718
What does this Scripture
has to do with this case?

1701
01:37:38,302 --> 01:37:40,221
Your Honor,
if I may continue?

1702
01:37:40,221 --> 01:37:41,689
(Judge King)
All right, go ahead.

1703
01:37:41,689 --> 01:37:44,191
I understand this is not
church and I'm not a preacher,

1704
01:37:44,191 --> 01:37:47,978
but this is a place of justice
and justice is found

1705
01:37:47,978 --> 01:37:49,480
in these living Words.

1706
01:37:49,480 --> 01:37:52,199
This Scripture says that
the reason that you see so many

1707
01:37:52,199 --> 01:37:56,287
cases and that I work so many
cases is because our marriages

1708
01:37:56,287 --> 01:38:01,292
in this society have no hope
because they have no character.

1709
01:38:01,292 --> 01:38:05,079
And today, true justice
is through hope.

1710
01:38:05,079 --> 01:38:06,997
And just as this Scripture says
that hope will not disappoint,

1711
01:38:06,997 --> 01:38:13,554
today my client receives
hope and she understands,

1712
01:38:13,554 --> 01:38:15,506
just as perhaps many of
the marriages that are

1713
01:38:15,506 --> 01:38:17,892
hanging on by the last thread
need to understand,

1714
01:38:18,392 --> 01:38:20,227
that it's not time
to run from our problems,

1715
01:38:20,761 --> 01:38:24,181
but to run through our
problems and to persevere.

1716
01:38:24,181 --> 01:38:27,685
Divorce doesn't fix things,
it doesn't solve problems.

1717
01:38:27,685 --> 01:38:29,186
Love is the answer.

1718
01:38:29,687 --> 01:38:32,690
Today, my client is
in the right place.

1719
01:38:32,690 --> 01:38:34,441
(Judge King)
And where's this?

1720
01:38:34,441 --> 01:38:36,277
(attorney)
At home where she belongs
because she's heard

1721
01:38:36,777 --> 01:38:40,781
this living Word that
perseverance gives character

1722
01:38:40,781 --> 01:38:42,750
and character hope.

1723
01:38:43,250 --> 01:38:45,252
Well, I can see your client
obviously found the hope

1724
01:38:45,252 --> 01:38:49,540
that she was looking
for 'cause she's not here.

1725
01:38:49,540 --> 01:38:53,043
So the case resets
6 months from today.

1726
01:38:55,546 --> 01:38:56,046
How do you feel?

1727
01:38:56,547 --> 01:38:57,848
Better.
Much better.

1728
01:38:57,848 --> 01:38:59,266
Good, good.

1729
01:38:59,266 --> 01:39:01,352
It's been over a week
Yes. now since the surgery.

1730
01:39:01,352 --> 01:39:02,303
You'll be ready to leave
the hospital very soon.

1731
01:39:02,803 --> 01:39:05,940
Oh, by the way, you asked
about the kidney donor?

1732
01:39:05,940 --> 01:39:09,610
Mr. Taylor is already recovering
back home very nicely.

1733
01:39:09,610 --> 01:39:11,028
Taylor?

1734
01:39:11,028 --> 01:39:15,532
Mr. Joshua Taylor from,
I believe, Lancaster, Iowa?

1735
01:39:15,532 --> 01:39:16,483
There must be some mistake.

1736
01:39:16,483 --> 01:39:18,736
No mistake, ma'am.

1737
01:39:18,736 --> 01:39:20,404
Is there a problem?

1738
01:39:20,404 --> 01:39:22,957
Yes.
That's my son.

1739
01:39:22,957 --> 01:39:23,457
I can't believe that he--

1740
01:39:23,457 --> 01:39:26,994
Excuse me.

1741
01:39:35,302 --> 01:39:37,421
Mrs. Lucille, we've just
received some news from

1742
01:39:37,421 --> 01:39:41,475
the doctor taking care of
your son back home in Iowa,

1743
01:39:41,925 --> 01:39:43,510
Joshua Taylor.

1744
01:39:44,061 --> 01:39:46,230
Apparently he
was recovering back home

1745
01:39:46,230 --> 01:39:50,517
and collapsed apparently
from a brain aneurysm.

1746
01:39:52,736 --> 01:39:55,739
No one knew about it.

1747
01:39:55,739 --> 01:39:57,741
I'm so sorry, ma'am.

1748
01:39:57,741 --> 01:40:00,027
He didn't make it.

1749
01:40:00,027 --> 01:40:04,448
[crying]

1750
01:40:04,448 --> 01:40:09,503
♪♪♪

1751
01:40:10,871 --> 01:40:13,707
That can't be!

1752
01:40:14,708 --> 01:40:30,024
♪♪♪

1753
01:40:44,371 --> 01:40:46,373
It is an amazing thing that
life should be punctuated

1754
01:40:46,373 --> 01:40:49,376
by moments such as these.

1755
01:40:49,376 --> 01:40:53,380
Today we're here to honor
and to remember

1756
01:40:53,881 --> 01:40:57,384
our loved one,
Joshua Taylor.

1757
01:40:57,384 --> 01:41:01,388
He was a young man whom some
of us might have thought

1758
01:41:01,388 --> 01:41:05,142
would have a long life
ahead of him.

1759
01:41:05,142 --> 01:41:07,644
And yet today we are reminded
that life--

1760
01:41:07,644 --> 01:41:09,646
The Bible also makes it clear

1761
01:41:09,646 --> 01:41:13,150
that we are by
nature children of wrath.

1762
01:41:13,150 --> 01:41:15,652
Hell is our destiny
unless someone--

1763
01:41:15,652 --> 01:41:19,156
Joshua Taylor discovered
to his great benefit

1764
01:41:19,156 --> 01:41:21,158
that the only way
that he could go to heaven

1765
01:41:21,158 --> 01:41:23,160
was through
faith in Christ alone.

1766
01:41:23,160 --> 01:41:26,663
Do you know that Jesus came
to this world to die for you?

1767
01:41:26,663 --> 01:41:28,165
He didn't just come
to be an example,

1768
01:41:28,165 --> 01:41:31,118
he came to be the lamb of God
who takes away

1769
01:41:31,118 --> 01:41:32,669
the sin of the world.

1770
01:41:32,669 --> 01:41:34,171
He came specifically to be
our redeeming sacrifice,

1771
01:41:34,671 --> 01:41:38,675
paying for our debt, making
possible our salvation

1772
01:41:38,675 --> 01:41:43,797
if we will but receive him
